# Task S55-T5: Map Types and Controls

## Description
1. Move the Map Type selection control to the right side of the screen (it's currently on the left). The client feels it's more familiar and easier to handle there.
2. Add a simple "Google Map" visual type to the available tile layers.
3. Return the "Settings (Gear)" icon to all tabs (it currently only exists on the Objects tab, but used to be on all tabs in the old app).

## Acceptance Criteria
- Map controls perfectly mirror expected alignment.
- Google Map tile layer works alongside existing maps (e.g. standard vector/OSM).
- Every major navigation tab exposes the gear icon with standard interactions.
